@startuml sq_agt01_execute_user_task
' ============================================================
' Title:     AGT-01 — PROCESS User Task
' Boundary:  nasim code agent CLI
' Purpose:   Core agentic loop: LLM call -> tool dispatch -> repeat
' Milestone: v1.0
' Version:   2.0.0
' Source:    docs/audit/audit_2026-06-20_capability-and-architecture.md
' Review:    —
' ============================================================

actor "Developer" as user

box "CLI Layer" #E8F5E9
  participant "REPLSession" as repl
end box
box "Agent Layer" #E3F2FD
  participant "AgentOrchestrator" as agent
  participant "ConversationHistory" as history
end box
box "Provider Layer" #FFF3E0
  participant "Provider" as provider
end box
box "Tool Layer" #F3E5F5
  participant "ToolRegistry" as tool
end box
box "Safety Layer" #FFF9C4
  participant "PermissionGate" as gate
end box

note over user, gate
  Scope:
    - agt01 PROCESS User Task — single complete task execution cycle

  Preconditions:
    - Agent initialized with Provider, ToolRegistry, ConversationHistory
    - Provider is reachable (network available)
    - Config loaded with valid provider + model settings

  Contexts:
    - Called by CLI-01 (PROCESS User Input) after REPL input parsed
    - Entry point for the entire agentic loop

  Excludes:
    - Slash command handling (CLI-02 handles those)
    - Streaming display rendering (CLI-03 handles those)
    - Session save/load (SSN-01/02 handles those)

  Rollback:
    - LLM call failure → append error message → ERROR state → IDLE
    - Tool execution failure → append error message → ERROR state → IDLE
    - Max iterations exceeded → force Done event

  Design:
    - AgentOrchestrator yields AgentEvent objects (no print())
    - Max iterations configurable via Config.max_iterations
    - ConversationHistory tracks token count for compaction trigger
    - PermissionGate consulted before every tool execution
    - Recursive: after tool dispatch, re-calls Provider for next response

  Returns:
    - Success: Done event with final text response
    - Failure: Error event with error description
end note

== agt01 PROCESS User Task ==

user -> repl : types input
repl -> agent : PROCESS(user_input)
activate agent

agent -> history : append user message to messages
activate history
history --> agent : messages updated
deactivate history

ref over agent, provider
  prv02: Call Provider Chat (or prv03: STREAM)
end ref

alt LLM returns text only
    agent -> history : append assistant message to messages
    activate history
    history --> agent : messages updated
    deactivate history
    agent --> repl : AgentEvent(Done)
else LLM returns tool calls
    agent -> history : append assistant message with tool_calls
    activate history
    history --> agent : messages updated
    deactivate history
    loop for each tool_call
        ref over agent, tool
          agt02: DISPATCH Tool Call
        end ref
    end
    ref over agent, provider
      prv02: Call Provider Chat [recurse — agt01 loops]
    end ref
    agent -> history : append assistant message to messages
    activate history
    history --> agent : messages updated
    deactivate history
    agent --> repl : AgentEvent(Done)
end

break LLM call fails or tool execution errors
    agent -> history : append error message
    activate history
    history --> agent : messages updated
    deactivate history
    agent --> repl : AgentEvent(Error)
end

deactivate agent

note over user, gate
  Flow:
    - User → REPLSession → AgentOrchestrator → Provider → (tool loop) → Done

  State:
    - IDLE → LISTENING → THINKING → [TOOL_EXEC]* → RESPONDING → IDLE

  Failure:
    - LLM error or tool error → ERROR → IDLE

  Success:
    - Done event with final text response

  Key invariants:
    - AgentOrchestrator never prints directly
    - Every tool call goes through PermissionGate
    - ConversationHistory owns message list integrity
end note

@enduml
